statements: SELECT * FROM vocal_exercises;
SELECT exercise_name, difficulty_level, duration_minutes FROM vocal_exercises ORDER BY difficulty_level DESC;
SELECT exercise_name, recommended_tempo FROM vocal_exercises WHERE duration_minutes > 15;
SELECT exercise_id, exercise_name, target_vocal_range FROM vocal_exercises WHERE recommended_tempo BETWEEN 80 AND 100;
SELECT exercise_name, instructions FROM vocal_exercises WHERE target_vocal_range = 'Soprano';
SELECT * FROM vocal_exercises ORDER BY exercise_name ASC, difficulty_level DESC;
SELECT exercise_name, duration_minutes, recommended_tempo FROM vocal_exercises WHERE difficulty_level > 3;
SELECT exercise_name, recommended_tempo, target_vocal_range FROM vocal_exercises WHERE recommended_tempo BETWEEN 60 AND 80;
SELECT * FROM vocal_exercises WHERE target_vocal_range LIKE 'Soprano%' ORDER BY duration_minutes DESC;
SELECT exercise_name, instructions FROM vocal_exercises WHERE difficulty_level < 2 AND duration_minutes < 5 ORDER BY exercise_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM vocal_exercises;
SELECT exercise_name, difficulty_level FROM vocal_exercises WHERE difficulty_level > 3;

SELECT exercise_name, duration_minutes FROM vocal_exercises ORDER BY duration_minutes DESC;
SELECT * FROM vocal_exercises WHERE difficulty_level = 3 ORDER BY exercise_name ASC;

SELECT singer_name, exercise_name, duration_minutes FROM singer_profiles JOIN vocal_exercises ON singer_profiles.preferred_exercise_id = vocal_exercises.exercise_id;
SELECT exercise_name, difficulty_level FROM vocal_exercises WHERE duration_minutes > 20 ORDER BY difficulty_level DESC, exercise_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM vocal_exercises WHERE exercise_name LIKE '%warmup%' AND difficulty_level < 4 ORDER BY exercise_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM Vocalists;
SELECT first_name, last_name, vocal_range FROM Vocalists ORDER BY vocal_range DESC;
SELECT first_name, last_name FROM Vocalists WHERE vocal_range='Soprano';
SELECT warmup_name, duration_minutes FROM Warmups WHERE difficulty_level > 3 ORDER BY duration_minutes ASC;

SELECT first_name, last_name, warmup_name, date_completed FROM Vocalists v JOIN VocalistWarmups vw ON v.vocalist_id = vw.vocalist_id JOIN Warmups w ON vw.warmup_id = w.warmup_id ORDER BY date_completed DESC;
SELECT * FROM Vocalists;
SELECT first_name, last_name, vocal_range FROM Vocalists WHERE vocal_range = 'Tenor';
SELECT first_name, last_name, vocal_range, warmup_name FROM Vocalists v JOIN VocalistWarmups vw ON v.vocalist_id = vw.vocalist_id JOIN Warmups w ON vw.warmup_id = w.warmup_id;
SELECT v.first_name, v.last_name, w.warmup_name, w.duration_minutes FROM Vocalists v LEFT JOIN VocalistWarmups vw ON v.vocalist_id = vw.vocalist_id LEFT JOIN Warmups w ON vw.warmup_id = w.warmup_id;
SELECT v.first_name, v.last_name, vw.date_completed FROM Vocalists v JOIN VocalistWarmups vw ON v.vocalist_id = vw.vocalist_id WHERE v.preferred_warmup_id IS NOT NULL;
SELECT * FROM exercises;
SELECT exercise_name, difficulty_level FROM exercises WHERE difficulty_level > 3;
SELECT singer_name, voice_type FROM singers WHERE voice_type = 'Soprano';
SELECT singer_name, experience_level FROM singers ORDER BY experience_level DESC;
SELECT exercise_name, duration_minutes FROM exercises WHERE duration_minutes BETWEEN 20 AND 30;
SELECT * FROM exercises ORDER BY exercise_name DESC;
SELECT singer_name, voice_type FROM singers WHERE experience_level = 'Intermediate';

SELECT singer_name, exercise_name FROM singers JOIN singer_exercises ON singers.singer_id = singer_exercises.singer_id JOIN exercises ON singer_exercises.exercise_id = exercises.exercise_id WHERE duration_minutes > 30;
SELECT singer_name, AVG(rating) AS avg_rating FROM singers JOIN exercise_ratings ON singers.singer_id = exercise_ratings.singer_id GROUP BY singer_name HAVING AVG(rating) > 4;

SELECT COUNT(singer_id) AS num_singers, AVG(difficulty_level) AS avg_difficulty FROM singer_exercises JOIN exercises ON singer_exercises.exercise_id = exercises.exercise_id GROUP BY exercise_name HAVING num_singers > 5 ORDER BY avg_difficulty DESC;
